# Sliding Window Problems

This folder contains solutions to important LeetCode problems based on the **Sliding Window technique**.

## 📌 Topics Covered

* Variable size window
* Fixed size window
* Two pointer technique
* Substring problems

## 🚀 Problems Included

1. Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters

## 🧠 Approach

Sliding Window is used to optimize problems involving subarrays or substrings by maintaining a window and adjusting its size dynamically.

## 🎯 Goal

To master efficient techniques for handling continuous subarrays and improve time complexity from O(n²) to O(n).
